        ><br />
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aCA6wknQsqg" target="_blank"
          >Easy D.I.Y Bird Feeder - How to Attract Birds to Your Garden
          (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-11539 mb-requirement-id-11541">
        (b) Build a birdbath and put it in an appropriate place. <br /><i
          >Resources:</i
        >
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yZl2N2XlHDA" target="_blank"
          >How to Pick (or Build) the Right Bird Bath for Your Garden (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/shorts/gJB3kN3xk6Y" target="_blank"
          >Easy DIY Bird Baths for Your Garden (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-11539 mb-requirement-id-11542">
        (c) Build a backyard sanctuary for birds by planting trees and shrubs
        for food and cover. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bjx4V1zcv2U" target="_blank"
          >How to Create a Bird Friendly Backyard (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bIqECrfp7HM" target="_blank"
          >What Happens When You Create a Bird Sanctuary in Your Backyard?
          (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ITHgy8xhIV0&t=285s"
          target="_blank"
          >Attract Backyard Birds With an Ecosystem Approach! (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-11539 mb-requirement-id-11543">
        (d) Build a nest box for a species of your choice using plans approved
        by your counselor. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u4iAhnbWpz8" target="_blank"
          >DIY Birdhouse (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j0werPvrrPI" target="_blank"
          >Build a Bird House for Under $5 in Under 5 Minutes (video)</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-11544">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 10. </span>
      Do the following:
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-11544 mb-requirement-id-11545">
        (a) Explain the differences between extinct, endangered, and threatened.
